  "time_ut": 1661232402,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd3\u0da8 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dc1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dab\u0dba \u0d86\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A student loan assistance scheme for science faculty students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Cabinet of Ministers has approved the establishment of a student loan assistance system under a subsidized interest basis for students undergoing training in the National Faculties of Education.",
        "This decision has been taken as the monthly allowance of Rs 5,000 currently being paid to them is insufficient.",
        "In addition to that allowance, a financial provision of a maximum of 10,000 rupees per month will be provided by a state bank on subsidized interest basis."
      ],
